<!-- Section 20: Risks and Mitigations -->
<section data-section="risks" class="proposal-section hidden">
  <div class="proposal-content">
    <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-[#1B2A4A] mb-6">20. Risks and Mitigations</h2>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-6">
      <table class="w-full text-sm border-collapse">
        <thead class="bg-[#1B2A4A] text-white">
          <tr>
            <th class="px-3 py-2 text-left font-medium">Risk</th>
            <th class="px-3 py-2 text-left font-medium">Likelihood</th>
            <th class="px-3 py-2 text-left font-medium">Impact</th>
            <th class="px-3 py-2 text-left font-medium">Mitigation</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr class="bg-white">
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2"><strong>SharePoint data quality issues</strong> (missing fields, inconsistent formats)</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2"><span class="inline-block px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-medium bg-red-100 text-red-700">High</span></td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2"><span class="inline-block px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-medium bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-700">Medium</span></td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">Validation layer with detailed error logging. Sync status visible in UI. Invalid records logged, never silently dropped. Validate real data quality in Discovery.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50">
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2"><strong>SharePoint API throttling during large syncs</strong></td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2"><span class="inline-block px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-medium bg-red-100 text-red-700">High</span></td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2"><span class="inline-block px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-medium bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-700">Medium</span></td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">Delta queries minimise API calls. Microsoft Graph SDK handles Retry-After headers automatically. Schedule syncs outside business hours.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-white">
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2"><strong>Scope creep from MLP features into MVP</strong></td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2"><span class="inline-block px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-medium bg-red-100 text-red-700">High</span></td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2"><span class="inline-block px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-medium bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-700">Medium</span></td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">Clear scope boundary in this document. Change request process for additions. Weekly demos keep scope visible.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50">
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2"><strong>Graph rendering performance with large datasets</strong> (500+ nodes)</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2"><span class="inline-block px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-medium bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-700">Medium</span></td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2"><span class="inline-block px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-medium bg-red-100 text-red-700">High</span></td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">fcose layout (2x faster than CoSE), viewport culling, level-of-detail rendering, layout caching. Determine actual data scale in Discovery.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-white">
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2"><strong>Client IT delays for Entra consent and SharePoint access</strong></td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2"><span class="inline-block px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-medium bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-700">Medium</span></td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2"><span class="inline-block px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-medium bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-700">Medium</span></td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">Clear step-by-step guides with screenshots. Minimise required client IT actions. Screen-share walkthrough for first onboarding.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50">
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2"><strong>Technical lead not appointed</strong> (TBC in RFP)</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2"><span class="inline-block px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-medium bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-700">Medium</span></td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2"><span class="inline-block px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-medium bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-700">Medium</span></td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">Escalate early. Proceed with BrightKeep recommendations subject to Cloud9 review.</td>
